" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wmu1665702708557.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmu1665702708557.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmu1665702708557.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wmu1665702708557\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Drag-and-Drop Format\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Drag-and-Drop Format is Development Object that defines a default action, pop-up menu, and icon that can be used when performing drag-and-drop actions in the tree and picture widgets of forms. It is not used for drag-and-drop widgets.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__section_w317ab1b5b1_w318ab1b5_w319ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__section_w320ab1b5b3_w321ab1b5_w322ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268387e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fmt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormatName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>.fmt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmu1665702708557__table_d10685e1_d10686e1_d10687e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>:fmt<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormatName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__section_w323ab1b5b5_w324ab1b5_w325ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268387e258\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__p_d96215e1_d96216e1_d96217e1\">Drag-and-Drop Format specializes Development Object in\n            the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38969e1_d38970e1_d38971e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__p_d96218e1_d96219e1_d96220e1\">It has a runtime library as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38972e1_d38973e1_d38974e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__p_d96221e1_d96222e1_d96223e1\">It has no child development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__section_w326ab1b5b7_w327ab1b5_w328ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268387e282\"> Properties </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38975e1_d38976e1_d38977e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38978e1_d38979e1_d38980e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cfv1665702708639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cfv1665702708639.html\" title=\"Language code for the global object with which you are working.\">Language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38981e1_d38982e1_d38983e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38984e1_d38985e1_d38986e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mzt1665702708708.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mzt1665702708708.html\" title=\"Default action when the selected object is dragged and dropped. Valid values are Copy, Move, or Create Shortcut. When the pop-up menu is displayed during a drag and drop action, the default action is shown in bold.\">Default Action</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38987e1_d38988e1_d38989e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ayn1665702708779.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ayn1665702708779.html\" title=\"Text to be displayed for the related action in the pop-up menu of the drag-and-drop format.\">Option Text</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38990e1_d38991e1_d38992e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fii1665702708857.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fii1665702708857.html\" title=\"Type of image to use as a background or icon—Glyph or File.\">Mouse Pointer Icon</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmu1665702708557__li_d38993e1_d38994e1_d38995e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616755\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616755\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Drag-and-Drop Format Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Drag-and-Drop Format A Drag-and-Drop Format is Development Object that defines a default action, pop-up menu, and icon that can be used when performing drag-and-drop actions in the tree and picture widgets of forms. It is not used for drag-and-drop widgets. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: fmt Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: FormatName @ LibraryName @ Language .fmt URI format: lib: LibraryName . Language :fmt FormatName Specialization Drag-and-Drop Format specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a runtime library as parent. It has no child development objects. Properties Name Language Description Default Action Option Text Mouse Pointer Icon Comments Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}